28.             <dt>Location</dt>
29.             <dd>@_shipment.Location</dd>
30.             <dt>Estimated Delivery</dt>
31.             <dd>@_shipment.EstimatedDelivery.ToString("f")</dd>
32.         </dl>
33. 
